  "texts": [
    "The workflow of manual annotation is shown in Fig. 1.",
    "The whole annotating process was started with literature search on PubMed.",
    "There were four steps to retrieve interested articles: (1) Specific genes and the word of \"mutation\" were searched as key words on https:// pubmed. ncbi.",
    "Specific genes referred to the common genes such as SMN1, DMD, PAH and G6PD in common single gene diseases or hereditary cancers.",
    "(2) The results were divided into subgroups of five years with the \"RESULTS BY YEAR\" filter and only full texts were selected with the \"Free full text\" option in the \"TEXT AVAILABILITY\" category."
  ],
